{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"78c40b9e4a","title":"北京钢铁学院发现反动标语","origin":"中共中央宣传部《宣教动态》1956年第25期。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"270b937836","index":0,"year":1956,"month":11,"day":4,"articleId":"78c40b9e4a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"57fa7e3598","type":"title","text":"北京钢铁学院发现反动标语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"78c40b9e4a"},{"id":"eec4ef3ce2","type":"paragraph","text":"北京钢铁学院学委会反映：十月二十九日上午七点半在该校饭厅及主楼、九楼发现有人用粉笔写有五条标语：1、中国人处在悲惨情景，青年们行动起来吧！2、支持匈波人民的斗争；3、反对目前的社会主义制度；4、我们要民主、自主；5、要民主！要写标语的地方还画了一些看不清的图样，好像是手枪笔。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"78c40b9e4a"},{"id":"2b0653566f","type":"paragraph","text":"另外，该院在普选时，曾发现选票上有人写高岗的名字。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"78c40b9e4a"}],"page":{"id":"900601e947","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"78c40b9e4a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}